'''''Place of Weeping''''' (ikinamico nka '''Afrika - Land der Hoffnung''' )<ref>THE SCREEN: 'PLACE OF WEEPING' - The New York Times <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 1986/12/05 › movies › the-scr...</ref>, ni filime y'ikinamico yo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afrika yepfo]] yasohotse muri 1986 yayobowe na Darrell Roodt ikanakorwa na Anant Singh muri Place of Weeping Productions<ref>Place of Weeping - Cleveland International Film Festival <nowiki>https://www.clevelandfilm.org</nowiki> › films › place-of-weeping</ref>.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo James Whyle, Gcina Mhlophe na Charles Comyn mu bakinnyi ba mbere mu gihe Norman Coombes, Michelle du Toit, Kerneels Coertzen na Patrick Shai bagize uruhare runini<ref>Place of Weeping Reviews - TV Guide <nowiki>https://www.tvguide.com</nowiki> › place-of-weeping › review</ref><ref>Place of Weeping Movie Poster - IMP Awards <nowiki>http://www.impawards.com</nowiki> › place_of_weeping</ref>.   Iyi filime isobanura mu buryo burambuye ku matsinda y’imico myinshi yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo n’uburyo [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo yaguye kubera ibikorwa by’abanyafurika yepfo n’amakimbirane mu butegetsi bukandamiza [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo<ref>a place for weeping - MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › a-place-for-weeping</ref>. Iyi niyo shusho yambere yo kurwanya ivanguramoko yakozwe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo<ref>A Place for Weeping (1986) - Filmaffinity <nowiki>https://www.filmaffinity.com</nowiki> › film335425</ref>. Filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku ya 5 Ukuboza 1986. Filime yakiriwe neza nabayireba<ref>Place of Weeping (1986) — The Movie Database (TMDB) <nowiki>https://www.themoviedb.org</nowiki> › movie › 568475-place-o...</ref>.  

